{"tid":577781,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"徹底被羞辱！雲格鏡頭前「抹眼淚」","createTime":"2018-03-02T05:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T19:37:30.000Z","uid":4661,"like":197,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"46d029b36ab44154d58815094d46d0c1bc9a3880","tid":577781,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T05:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180302/photo/bkn-20180302091323849-0302_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180302093548\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180302091323849-0302_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180302093548&h=c074edbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴喺英超主場以0:3不敵曼城，繼英聯盃決賽後再次淨吞對手3蛋徹底被羞辱，而且有傳媒話，兵工廠領隊雲格喺比賽期間「抹眼淚」，仲曾經用手擋住自己塊面，避免畀電視鏡頭影到佢老淚縱橫嘅場面。雖然畫面所見，好難斷定到底雲格有冇流出眼淚，不過奠長球場出現大量空位，疑似有廠迷集體拒絕入場罷睇，同埋有好多球迷喺阿仙奴無力反抗下，冇癮選擇提早離場，相信雲格內心嘅悽楚，大家或多或少都可以感受到。"},{"pid":"7180926ee1e5c62582cf8aa4fc09e1bbfe3355d8","tid":577781,"uid":34571,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T05:04:24.000Z","msg":"掩面笑緊"},{"pid":"b17d4474d37b1d58a7338edcaa584c8017a80901","tid":577781,"uid":20634,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T05:04:40.000Z","msg":"眼訓姐"},{"pid":"ae29aa392b8c020912655aac3728a7fc0c671c5a","tid":577781,"uid":31354,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"7180926ee1e5c62582cf8aa4fc09e1bbfe3355d8","tid":577781,"uid":34571,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T05:04:24.000Z","msg":"掩面笑緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T05:05:35.000Z","msg":"下個禮拜搵隊a貨米蘭出氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266c597e541c423545b34fc6f3ab037bcba6037c","tid":577781,"uid